[SHORT DESC]
30% chance to poison.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Has a 30% chance to poison the target.
</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/moves/thunder">Thunder</a> is an Electric-type equivalent, but with a chance to paralyze, though special.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/fire_blast">Fire Blast</a> is a Fire-type equivalent, but with a chance to burn and more accuracy, though special.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/blizzard">Blizzard</a> is an Ice-type equivalent with a chance to freeze, though special.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/hydro_pump">Hydro Pump</a> is a Water-type equivalent, but does not have an effect and has more accuracy, though special.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/gunk_shot">Focus Blast</a> is a Fighting-type equivalent with a chance to lower Special Defense, though special.</p>